WEBVTT

00:00:28.397 --> 00:00:30.217
broj ljudi u prostoriji?

00:00:30.217 --> 00:00:31.382
Pa, ako ste kao ja,

00:00:31.382 --> 00:00:33.148
vjerojatno biste pokazali na svaku osobu,

00:00:33.148 --> 00:00:34.028
jednu po jednu,

00:00:34.028 --> 00:00:35.725
i brojali od 0:

00:00:35.725 --> 00:00:38.528
1, 2, 3, 4 i tako dalje.

00:00:38.528 --> 00:00:39.621
Dakle, to je algoritam.

00:00:39.621 --> 00:00:40.955
Zapravo, probajmo to izraziti

00:00:40.955 --> 00:00:42.824
malo formalnije u pseudokodu,

00:00:42.824 --> 00:00:44.075
sintaksi sličnoj engleskom

00:00:44.075 --> 00:00:46.029
koja nalikuje na programski jezik.

00:00:46.029 --> 00:00:47.796
Neka je n jednako 0.

00:00:47.796 --> 00:00:52.548
Za svaku osobu u prostoriji,
skup n = n + 1.

00:00:52.548 --> 00:00:54.085
Kako protumačiti ovaj pseudokod?

00:00:54.085 --> 00:00:55.921
Pa, redak 1 izjavljuje, tako reći,

00:00:55.921 --> 00:00:57.337
varijablu nazvanu n

00:00:57.337 --> 00:00:59.716
i započinje svoju vrijednost na 0.

00:00:59.716 --> 00:01:02.051
Ovo samo znači da na početku
našeg algoritma,